ActFamily Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Family Support Orders and Agreements Garnishment Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the FAMILY SUPPORT ORDERS AND AGREEMENTS GARNISHMENT REGULATIONS in order to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of the Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act Part II garnishment scheme, maintain its relevancy, reflect current practices and continue to support federal, provincial and territorial cooperation in the area of support enforcement.
